ser support</h4>\n<p><span class=\"snippet__support-note\">⚠️ Not supported in IE11 or the current version of Edge.</span></p>\n<!-- Whenever possible, link a `caniuse` feature which allows the browser support percentage to be displayed.\nIf no link is provided, it defaults to 99+%. -->\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#feat=css-focus-within\">https://caniuse.com/#feat=css-focus-within</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Focus Within","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/focus-within/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/fullscreen/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Fullscreen"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/flexbox-centering/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Flexbox centering"}}}}}